rComments: Loved his teaching style, was open, engaging and challenging. Definitely one of the best classes I've had!
Attends to questions/concerns very well, interactive with the students, cool guy overall. Plus he's not bad on the eyes!

Seems like a really good guy. Pretty funny and respects the students. Lectures go by fairly quick and he opens the floor for some interesting discussions. Has a good sense as to when to cut off discussions and move forward
